            "text_6diUJT": {
              "type": "text",
              "name": "t:names.description",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<h4></h4><h3>Own Your Bookings</h3><p>No more redirecting customers to third-party booking engines. Keep them on your branded website from browsing to payment confirmation. Capture 100% of your customer information for email marketing, remarketing, and building direct relationships.</p><h3>Payment-enabled Itineraries</h3><p>Transform Wetu itineraries into bookable contracts with online payment on your website.</p><h3>Get Paid Faster</h3><p>Setup an account payment gateways like Peach Payments or Payfast. Funds settle directly to your bank account in 1-2 days—no waiting for platform payouts.</p><p></p><h3>Multi-Language</h3><p>Reach global travelers with up to 20 languages, improving conversion and SEO.</p><p></p>",
